\pard\f0\fs30 M\'ecnh h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c c\u7845?p ba \u7903? m\u7897?t tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng n\u7897?i tr\f0\lang1033\'fa n\f1\lang1066\u7893?i ti\u7871?ng \u7903? Trung Qu\u7889?c - United World College Changshu China. Tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng t\u7915?ng hai l\u7847?n \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7873? c\u7917? cho gi\u7843?i Nobel H\f0\lang1033\'f2a B\'ecnh v\'e0 c\'f3 r\f1\lang1066\u7845?t nhi\u7873?u c\u7921?u h\u7885?c sinh l\f0\lang1033\'e0 ch\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? gia, ho\f0\lang1033\'e0ng gia, nh\'e0 ho\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i, doanh nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n n\f1\lang1066\u7893?i ti\u7871?ng tr\f0\lang1033\'ean kh\f1\lang1066\u7855?p th\u7871? gi\u7899?i. S\u7913? m\u7879?nh c\u7911?a tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0 t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o ti\u7873?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7873? cho h\u7885?c sinh tr\u7903? th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng \ldblquote ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i t\u7841?o ra thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i\rdblquote  (change-makers) trong t\f2\u432?\u417?ng lai.\par
\par
V\f0\lang1033\'ec v\f1\lang1066\u7853?y, trong su\u7889?t hai n\f2\'e3m, t\f1\u7915? 17 \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n 19 tu\u7893?i, ng\f0\lang1033\'e0y n\'e0o m\'ecnh c\f2\u361?ng \'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c nh\u7855?c nh\u7903? v\u7873? \ldblquote s\u7913? m\u7879?nh\rdblquote  c\u7911?a tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \ldblquote\f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh m\u7879?nh\rdblquote  c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh. M\'ecnh nghe \f2\'f0i nghe l\f1\lang1066\u7841?i: \ldblquote M\f0\lang1033\'e0y c\f2\u361?ng s\f1\lang1066\u7869? tr\u7903? th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh \lquote change-maker\rquote , T\'f9ng \f1\lang1066\u7841?. M\f0\lang1033\'e0y may m\f1\lang1066\u7855?n l\u7855?m m\u7899?i \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c h\u7885?c \u7903? \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e2y, n\'ean m\'e0y c\'f3 ngh\f2\u297?a v\f1\lang1066\u7909? v\u7899?i th\u7871? gi\u7899?i hi\u7875?u kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng?\rdblquote\par
\par
V\'e0 m\'ecnh tin \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3. M\'ecnh th\f1\lang1066\u7845?m nhu\u7847?n c\f0\lang1033\'e1c gi\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7889?t l\f0\lang1033\'f5i c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng: ngh\f2\u297? cho c\f1\u7897?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7891?ng, c\u7889?ng hi\u7871?n cho x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i, v\f0\lang1033\'e0 thay \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i th\u7871? gi\u7899?i. \f2\'d0\f0\lang1033\'e2y l\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t \ldblquote g\f0\lang1033\'e1nh n\f1\lang1066\u7863?ng\rdblquote  kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ai \'e9p m\'ecnh ph\f1\lang1066\u7843?i mang, nh\f2\u432?ng m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh t\f1\lang1066\u7921? xem \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 l\'e0 tr\'e1ch nhi\f1\lang1066\u7879?m cho nh\u7919?ng m\f0\lang1033\'f3n qu\'e0 m\'ecnh \f2\'f0\f0\'e3 nh\f1\lang1066\u7853?n \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c t\u7915? qu\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\'ecnh theo h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c \u7903? UWC.\par
\par
M\f0\lang1033\'ecnh bi\f1\lang1066\u7871?t \f2\u417?n tr\u432?\f1\u7901?ng v\f0\lang1033\'ec \f2\'f0\f0\'e3 \f2\u432?\u417?m v\f0\'e0o suy ngh\f2\u297? c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? t\u7889?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7865?p nh\f2\u432? v\f1\u7853?y ngay t\u7915? khi m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh c\'f2n r\f1\lang1066\u7845?t tr\u7867?. V\f0\lang1033\'ec nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 n\f1\lang1066\u7871?u \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n l\f0\lang1033\'fac m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i ch\u7841?c 30, 40 tu\u7893?i, m\u7899?i c\u7889? g\u7855?ng truy\u7873?n cho h\u7885? s\u7869? r\u7845?t kh\f0\lang1033\'f3. Th\f1\lang1066\u7871? gi\u7899?i quan c\u7911?a m\u7897?t ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i tr\u7867? 18 tu\u7893?i d\u7877? thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i h\f2\u417?n nhi\f1\u7873?u. Nh\f2\u432?ng m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh c\f2\u361?ng \u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?c \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e3 c\'f3 ai \f2\'f0\f0\'f3 n\'f3i v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh \f1\lang1066\u7903? nh\u7919?ng n\f2\'e3m th\f0\lang1033\'e1ng \f1\lang1066\u7845?y l\f0\lang1033\'e0: \ldblquote C\'e1c em s\f1\lang1066\u7869? thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i th\u7871? gi\u7899?i. Nh\f2\u432?ng h\f0\lang1033\'e3y h\f1\lang1066\u7871?t s\u7913?c b\f0\lang1033\'ecnh t\f2\u297?nh, v\f0\'ec \f2\'f0\f0\'f3 l\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh tr\'ecnh d\'e0i - m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh tr\'ecnh c\f1\lang1066\u7843? m\u7897?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7901?i ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i.\rdblquote\par
\par
\b\fs50 T\u7847?m nh\f0\lang1033\'ecn xa v\'e0 nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng giai \f2\'f0o\f1\u7841?n c\u7911?a cu\u7897?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7901?i\b0\fs30\par
\f0\lang1033 Hai n\f2\'e3m sau khi t\f1\lang1066\u7889?t nghi\u7879?p UWC, c\f0\lang1033\'f3 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t cu\u7897?c g\u7863?p \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e3 thay \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i t\f2\u432? duy c\f1\u7889?ng hi\u7871?n c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh. Trong m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t b\u7919?a t\u7889?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0o th\'e1ng 10 n\f2\'e3m 2019, m\f0\'ecnh g\f1\lang1066\u7863?p Shelby Davis \f3\endash\f0  t\f1\u7927? ph\f0\lang1033\'fa t\'e0i tr\f1\lang1066\u7907? cho m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh \f2\'f0i h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c \u7903? M\u7929?. \f0\lang1033\'d4ng chia s\f1\lang1066\u7867? v\u7873? l\f0\lang1033\'fd do \'f4ng b\f1\lang1066\u7855?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u c\f0\lang1033\'e1c ho\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng t\u7915? thi\u7879?n su\u7889?t h\f2\u417?n 20 n\'e3m qua, gi\f0\lang1033\'fap h\f2\u417?n 14.000 h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c sinh t\u7889?t nghi\u7879?p UWC c\f0\lang1033\'f3 c\f2\u417? h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i h\u7885?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i h\u7885?c \u7903? M\u7929?.\par
\par
