\par
30 n\f2\'e3m \'f0\f1\lang1066\u7847?u l\f0\lang1033\'e0m g\'ec c\f2\u361?ng \'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c, nh\f2\u432?ng h\f1\u7885?c t\u7853?p l\f0\lang1033\'e0 quan tr\f1\lang1066\u7885?ng nh\u7845?t. 30 n\f2\'e3m sau l\f0\lang1033\'e0m g\'ec c\f2\u361?ng \'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c, nh\f2\u432?ng x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng n\u7873?n t\u7843?ng t\f0\lang1033\'e0i ch\'ednh l\'e0 \f2\u432?u ti\f0\'ean h\'e0ng \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7847?u. 30 n\f2\'e3m cu\f1\u7889?i l\f0\lang1033\'e0m g\'ec c\f2\u361?ng \'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c, nh\f2\u432?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0m t\f1\lang1066\u7915? thi\u7879?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0 cho \f2\'f0i l\f0\'e0 \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u s\u7869? khi\u7871?n ph\u7847?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7901?i c\f0\lang1033\'f2n l\f1\lang1066\u7841?i c\f0\lang1033\'f3 \'fd ngh\f2\u297?a.\par
\par
