\par
Nh\f2\u432?ng c\f0\'e0ng suy ng\f1\lang1066\u7851?m, m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh c\'e0ng hi\f1\lang1066\u7875?u v\u7873? m\u7913?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7897? quan tr\u7885?ng c\u7911?a m\u7897?t t\u7847?m nh\f0\lang1033\'ecn xa. Nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i (impact) \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n s\u7899?m nh\u7845?t ch\f2\u432?a ch\f1\u7855?c \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e3 l\'e0 thay \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i b\u7873?n v\u7919?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\'f3 gi\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? nh\u7845?t. B\u7903?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? th\u7921?c s\u7921? ki\u7871?n t\u7841?o thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i c\u7847?n ph\u7843?i ho\u7841?ch \f2\'f0\f1\u7883?nh trong m\u7897?t t\u7847?m nh\f0\lang1033\'ecn xa, m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh tr\'ecnh k\'e9o d\'e0i c\f1\lang1066\u7843? \f2\'f0\f1\u7901?i ch\u7913? kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ph\f1\lang1066\u7843?i c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?t \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c ch\u7881? trong ch\u7889?c l\f0\lang1033\'e1t.\par
\par
Gi\f1\lang1066\u7889?ng nh\f2\u432? c\f0\lang1033\'e2u chuy\f1\lang1066\u7879?n c\u7911?a Davis, n\u7871?u \f0\lang1033\'f4ng v\f1\lang1066\u7897?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0ng \ldblquote thay \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i th\u7871? gi\u7899?i\rdblquote  ngay khi t\u7889?t nghi\u7879?p \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i h\u7885?c Princeton, b\u7857?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch \f2\'f0i l\f0\'e0m t\'ecnh nguy\f1\lang1066\u7879?n vi\f0\lang1033\'ean \f1\lang1066\u7903? m\u7897?t t\u7893? ch\u7913?c phi ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh ph\f1\lang1066\u7911?, thay v\f0\lang1033\'ec t\f1\lang1066\u7853?p trung v\f0\lang1033\'e0o x\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng gia t\f0\lang1033\'e0i c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\'ec kh\f1\lang1066\u7843? n\f2\'e3ng cao 14,000 h\f1\u7885?c sinh t\u7889?t nghi\u7879?p UWC \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\f2\u417? h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i \f2\'f0i h\f1\u7885?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i h\u7885?c ti\u7871?p, v\f0\lang1033\'e0 t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o ra nh\u7919?ng thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i nh\f2\u432? b\f0\lang1033\'e2y gi\f1\lang1066\u7901?.\par
\par
Vi\u7879?c Davis ch\u7885?n \ldblquote thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i th\u7871? gi\u7899?i\rdblquote  tr\u7877? h\f2\u417?n ph\f1\u7847?n n\f0\lang1033\'e0o \f2\'f0\f0\'e3 khi\f1\lang1066\u7871?n \f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o n\f0\lang1033\'ean thay \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i m\u7841?nh m\u7869? h\f2\u417?n cho th\f1\u7871? gi\u7899?i c\u7911?a 14,000 ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i.\par
\par
